<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Preview no longer available</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-stone-50 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
<div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-8">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">This preview has ended.</h1>
  <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">
    For legal reasons the demo site was deleted after the review window closed.
    If you'd like it restored from a backup, fill out the form below and Daniel
    will follow up personally within one business day.
  </p>

  <form method="POST" action="/goodbye/restore-request" class="space-y-3">
    <input name="name" placeholder="Your name" class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded px-3 py-2" required>
    <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="Email" class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded px-3 py-2" required>
    <input name="phone" placeholder="Phone (optional)" class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded px-3 py-2">

    <fieldset class="pt-2">
      <legend class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-2">How would you prefer I reach out?</legend>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <input type="radio" name="preferred_contact" value="email" checked> Email
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <input type="radio" name="preferred_contact" value="phone"> Phone call
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <input type="radio" name="preferred_contact" value="text"> Text message
      </label>
    </fieldset>

    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-stone-900 hover:bg-stone-800 text-white rounded py-2 font-medium mt-4">
      Request restore from backup
    </button>
  </form>

  <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-6 text-center">
    BitBuilder Cloud LLC · daniel@bitbuilder.io · Denton, TX
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
